      "completenessGrade": "FULL",
      "sourceSnippet": "There is an increased risk of diabetic ketoacidosis conferred by SGLT2i; however, this is generally a rare event in T2D, occurring in < 1 per 1000 patient-years in a prior meta-analysis. In the CREDENCE trial, this was 2.2 versus 0.2 per 1000 patient-years for canagliflozin versus placebo.",
